{"type":"text","timestamp":1775870985269,"sessionID":"ses_285d90dd5ffeNChu9EQss5jz4F","part":{"id":"prt_d7a28a97a001kEf6paVZYpk2ih","messageID":"msg_d7a287ad4001Fzo9l3p1FxkgZz","sessionID":"ses_285d90dd5ffeNChu9EQss5jz4F","type":"text","text":"## Verification Results\n\n### Package Layout ✅\nAll required files exist and match spec:\n- `agentcube/__init__.py` - exports `CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`\n- `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` - exports 3 client classes\n- All client modules: `control_plane.py`, `code_interpreter_data_plane.py`, `agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n- Utility modules: `utils/http.py` (create_session), `utils/utils.py` (read_token_from_file), `utils/log.py` (get_logger)\n\n### Configuration ✅\nAll defaults match spec:\n- `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n- Environment variable resolution: `ROUTER_URL`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`\n- Token file fallback: `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n\n### API Contracts ✅\n- `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__` - matches spec signature with all params\n- `AgentRuntimeClient.__init__` - matches spec (router_url, timeout, connect_timeout, etc.)\n- `ControlPlaneClient` - base_url from workload_manager_url, Authorization header handling\n- Data plane clients accept base_url OR construct from router_url+namespace+name\n\n### Tests ✅\n**242 tests passed** (0 failures)\n\n### Issues Found\n\n| Category | Count | Details |\n|----------|-------|---------|\n| Lint (ruff) | ~50+ | Import sorting (I001), deprecated typing (UP006/UP035), unused imports (F401), B904 raise-from |\n| Typecheck (mypy) | ~25+ | Return type mismatches, optional→str assignments, argument type issues |\n\n**Note**: The spec mentions `utils/__init__.py` should be empty (module marker), but it has actual exports (`get_logger`, `read_token_from_file`). This is a minor deviation.\n\n**Conclusion**: Implementation matches spec requirements. All core functionality is correct, tests pass, but there are lint/typecheck issues that should be addressed for production quality.","time":{"start":1775870985267,"end":1775870985267}}}
